en.description: Sing 3 notes of major chord.
en.name: Major chords

ru.description: Пропойте 3 ноты мажорного аккорда.
ru.name: Мажорные аккорды

en.description: Singing major chord in five notes.
en.name: Detail singing of major chord

ru.description: Споем аккорд более расширенно.
ru.name: Опевание мажорного аккорда

en.description: The whole major scale is used in our song. Sing it and few nearby.
en.name: Chromatic major scale

ru.description: В песне полностью используется мажорная гамма. Спойте её и несколько соседних к ней гамм.
ru.name: Полная мажорная гамма

en.description: This movements of your voice are the smallest that you can do.
en.name: Semitones

ru.description: Эти движения голосом будут самыми маленькими из возможных в музыке.
ru.name: Полутона

en.description: This interval, which is using in this song, will be difficult for your voice.
en.name: Minor sixth

ru.description: Это непростой интервал, на котором строится один сложный ход в этой песне.
ru.name: Малая секста

en.description: We will start working with song from the firs part of the verse - first, it will sound single, and then we will add music instruments one by one.
en.name: First part of the verse

ru.description: Разберем по нотам первую половину куплета - сначала отдельно, потом постепенно добавляя к ней инструменты.
ru.name: Первая часть куплета

en.description: Now, the second part of the verse, it is almost the same.
en.name: Second part of the verse

ru.description: Теперь вторая часть куплета, она почти такая же по структуре.
ru.name: Вторая часть куплета

en.description: Sing all verse with accompaniment.
en.name: Whole verse with music

ru.description: Спойте весь куплет с аккомпанементом.
ru.name: Весь куплет с музыкой

en.description: Get ready to sing higher than you do before.
en.name: First part of the chorus

ru.description: Приготовьтесь петь выше, чем в куплете.
ru.name: Первая часть припева

en.description: Melody will look difficult, but it will go on the major scale, that you already start to learn.
en.name: Second part of the chorus

ru.description: Мелодия здесь будет сложнее, но  идти по обычной мажорной гамме, которую вы уже начали изучать.
ru.name: Вторая часть припева

en.description: Sing all chorus with accompaniment.
en.name: Whole chorus with music

ru.description: Спойте весь припев с аккомпанементом.
ru.name: Весь припев с музыкой

en.description: Melody is getting higher In the end with saving it’s form. Feel this transformation.
en.name: Modulation

ru.description: В конце песни форма мелодии сохраняется, но становится выше. Уловите этот переход.
ru.name: Модуляция

en.description: Entire song with arrangement.
en.midiText:
Strangers in the night
Exchanging glances
Wondering in the night
What were the chances
We'd be sharing love
Before the night was through?
Something in your eyes
Was so inviting
Something in your smile
Was so exciting
Something in my heart told me I must have you

Strangers in the night, two lonely people
We were strangers in the night
Up to the moment when we said our first hello
Little did we know
Love was just a glance away, a warm embracing dance away
And ever since that night
We've been together
Lovers at first sight
In love forever
It turned out so right
For strangers in the night

Love was just a glance away, a warm embracing dance away
Ever since that night
We've been together
Lovers at first sight
In love forever
It turned out so right
For strangers in the night

Doo-bee-doo-bee-doo
Doo-doo-dee-dah, dah-dah-dah-dah-dah
en.name: Song
